## Screen 3 — Task Detail / Contextual Help (supports Task 3 — H3)

```
[Page title: Task — "Meet your onboarding buddy"]
[Side nav: Overview | Day 1 | Week 1 | Documents | Help]

[Tile: Task details]
  [Text: description of the task]
  [Tag: AI recommended] [Text: "why this is recommended"]

[Card: Need a hand?]
  [Text: "Who to ask" — label]
  [Text: contact name]
  [Text: contact email/channel]

[Card: AI Assistant answer]
  [Text: sample answer]
  [Tag: "Source: Team Process Guide, updated yesterday"]
  [Note: "For HR, salary, or disciplinary questions, this hands off to a person"]

[Button: Mark complete]
[Button: Back to checklist]
```

